y subpoenas to several New York Times journalists? \n\nBecause the media wasn't just covering up the story. *They were part of the operation.*\n\nThe NYT reporters received the subpoenas because Military Intelligence has the digital footprints proving they were briefed on the \"aviation tragedy\" *before* Trump was even scheduled to board the plane. They had the pre-written articles ready to publish. \n\nThey were the cleanup crew. Now, they are co-conspirators in treason.\n\n**THE CLASSIFIED INTEL:**\n\u25aa\ufe0f **OPERATION-SKY-SHIELD** - The protocol that secured the President\n\u25aa\ufe0f **Subpoena-Alpha-7** - The active warrants for the media handlers\n\u25aa\ufe0f **Langley-Override** - The captured server data proving domestic coordination\n\nThe Deep State thought they could eliminate the Commander-in-Chief at 30,000 feet. Instead, they just handed Military Intelligence the exact coordinates of their entire domestic assassination network.\n\nDonald J. Trump\nState Of The Nation Live\nSilver Knight Broadcasting\nThe White House\nJustice by Truth", "author": "Hallelujah_Jesus", "created": 1783874448826, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "chickeninoven", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Is this for real?", "last_comment_created": 1783878617914, "content": "<p>Could This Be True?????</p>\n<p>THE DEEP STATE JUST TRIED TO TAKE DOWN AIR FORCE ONE. THEY FAILED. TRUMP KNEW.</p>\n<p>On July 9th, Donald J. Trump was scheduled to fly out of Turkey on the new Qatari-donated Boeing 747-8.</p>\n<p>At the last possible second, he switched to the old Air Force One. The media called it a &quot;security precaution.&quot;</p>\n<p>It wasn't a precaution. It was a counter-operation.</