se, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBqfDV3R", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 18, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8725399, "raw_content": "Not trying to Q-post or schizo-post here, but let's say that there was some treason afoot. Like release a virus to keep the deep state out of the gallows level treason. Publicly prosecuting it would confirm some of the government's bad actions in the past, and bad actors could leverage that against us. Mitch McConnell's wife leaves her husband's side when he is allegedly at his sickest. Must be urgent! She goes to meet with the CCP, basically. Couldn't this be done over the phone, lol? Of course not, she'd be arrested immediately, probably, if the contents of that conversation were leaked. Now Lindsey Graham was partners in crime with McCain in their poke-the-bear project in Ukraine. He makes one last trip to Ukraine, meets with Zelensky, comes back and is dead the next day. Maybe he went there to say \"it's over, they're executing us now\", maybe he was sent there by Trump. Maybe he was cooperating despite being a doomed man. His certain doom and cooperation would make sense of the bizarre defending of him by Trump when he was given a storm of boos when mentioning his name. Could it be happening? I'm crossing my fingers, but not holding my breath just yet.", "author": "DroolBuckets", "created": 1783884132946, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "sleepinggiant", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Two RINOs at Nearly the Same Time?", "last_comment_created": 1783886620604, "content": "<p>Not trying to Q-post or schizo-post here, but let's say that there was some treason afoot. Like release a virus to keep the deep state out of the gallows level treason. Publicly prosecuting it would confirm some of the government's bad actions in the past, and bad actors could leverage that against us. Mitch McConnell's wife leaves her husband's side when he is allegedly at his sickest. Must be urgent! She goes to meet with the CCP, basically. Couldn't this be done over the phone, lol? Of course not, she'd be arrested immediately, probably, if the contents of that conversation were leaked. Now Lindsey Graham was partners in crime with McCain in their poke-the-bear project in Ukraine. He makes one last trip to Ukraine, meets with Zelensky, comes back and is dead the next day. Maybe he went there to say &quot;it's over, they're executing us now&quot;, maybe he was sent there by Trump. Maybe he was cooperating despite being a doomed man. His certain doom and cooperation would make sense of the bizarre defending of him by Trump when he was given a storm of boos when mentioning his name. Could it be happening? I'm crossing my fingers, but not holding my breath just yet.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 18, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBqfCwQC", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 35, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8725110, "raw_content": "The Episcopalian Church goes first.  Then, about 45 minutes later, the Congregational bells ring.\n\nI can't imagine being woken up every fucking morning at 5 AM by goddamn Muslim call to prayers.", "author": "KuzoKevin", "created": 1783870970884, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2